<bibRefCitation author="Schuster, R. M." box="[443,623,294,320]" pageId="11" pageNumber="72" pagination="59 - 140" refId="ref20055" refString="Schuster, R. M. (1949) Contribution towards a monograph of the Mutillidae of the Neotropical region. III. A key to the subfamilies represented and descriptions of several new genera (Hymenoptera). Entomologica Americana, New Series, 29 (3 - 4), 59 - 140." type="journal article" year="1949">Schuster, 1949</bibRefCitation>
